==English==
===Phrasebook===
'''[[I'm]] in [[love]] with [[you]]'''

# Non-commital declaration of romantic feeling.

====Translations====
{{top}}
*[[Catalan]]: [[Estic enamorat de tu]] ''male speaker'', [[Estic enamorada de tu]] ''female speaker''
*Dutch: [[Ik ben verliefd op je]], [[Ik ben verliefd op jou]] ''for emphasis''
*Hungarian: [[Szerelmes vagyok beléd]]
*Irish Gaelic: [[Tá mé i ngrá leat]]
*Italian: [[Sono innamorato di te]] {{m}}, [[Sono innamorata di te]] {{f}}
*Japanese: [[好きです]] (suki desu)
*Persian (Farsi): [[من عاشقت هستم]] (man aasheghet hastam)
{{mid}}
*Korean: [[너를 사랑해]] (Neo-reul sarang-hae), [[당신이 좋아요]] (Dangsin-i joayo)
*Mongolian: [[Би чамд сайн]] (Bi chamd sain), [[Би чамд сэтгэлтэй болжээ]] (Bi chamd setgeltei boljee)
*Russian: [[Я полюбил тебя]] (ja poljubíl tebjá, ''male speaker''), [[Я полюбила тебя]] (ja poljubíla tebjá, ''female speaker'')
*Spanish: [[Estoy enamorado de ti]] ''male speaker'', [[Estoy enamorada de ti]] ''female speaker''
{{bottom}}

